            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Antoni<lb break="no" n="3"/>no <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>otestate</ex></expan> Parthico <lb n="6"/>Britannico <lb n="7"/>maximo <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Castius Avitus d<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="9"/>et IIvir <expan><abbr>Sol</abbr><ex>vae</ex></expan> ob hon<supplied reason="lost">orem</supplied> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>decurionat</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> ita ut <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>promis</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> ple</supplied><lb break="no" n="11"/>ne obtulit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unten abgebrochene Tafel, deren Rand abgearbeitet ist. Ehreninschrift für Kaiser Caracalla, gesetzt von C. Castius Avitus anläßlich seines Eintrittes in den Gemeinderat. Fundjahr: zwischen 1826 und 1831 in der zweiten Abbruchphase des Alten Turms. (B): Z. 3: Aug(usto) p(ontifici).</p>
            </div>
